title: Five Biggest Questions of the NFL Offseason
description:
Kevin and Nora are joined by The Ringer’s Kaelen Jones as they try to answer the biggest questions for the rest of the offseason (3:35), including where Aaron Rodgers will play next season (26:00), who could be the next big-name player traded (45:40), the impact of a 17-game season (54:00), and more.

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
Guest: Kaelen Jones
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
